11 one month of the issuance of a warning ticket shall be punishable as a Class 3
12 misdemeanor.
13 (2) For operating under an expired aquaculture operation permit, if the violation
14 occurs within one month of the expiration of the permit, the violation shall be
15 punishable only by issuance of a warning ticket pursuant to G.S. 113-140.
16 (3) For operating under an expired shellfish lease agreement, if the violation
17 occurs within one month of the expiration of the agreement, the violation shall
18 be punishable only by issuance of a warning ticket pursuant to G.S. 113-140."
19 SECTION 16.(b) This section becomes effective December 1, 2025, and applies to
20 offenses committed on or after that date.
